id: pm-2czc
title: "Unblock dependabot PRs: @types/node 26 type error, pnpm release-age cooldown, codeql-action lockstep group"
description: "All four open dependabot PRs (#459-#462) fail CI for three distinct root causes: (1) PR #462 exposes a real type error under @types/node 26 - drift-scan.ts cacheMetadataMatches typed stat as Awaited<ReturnType<typeof fs.stat>> which now widens to include undefined (TS18048); (2) PR #461 bumps eslint-plugin-unicorn 71.0.0 published ~6h before the run, rejected by pnpm 11 supply-chain minimum-release-age check (ERR_PNPM_MINIMUM_RELEASE_AGE_VIOLATION); (3) PRs #459/#460 bump codeql-action init/analyze in separate PRs so the Analyze job fails on 'configuration file for version 4.36.3 but running 4.36.2'."
type: Chore
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[4]: "area:ci",ci,dependabot,dependencies
created_at: "2026-07-06T08:45:16.538Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-06T21:07:58.246Z"
author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 60
acceptance_criteria: tsc clean under @types/node 22 and 26; dependabot npm bumps wait 3 days before opening PRs; codeql-action init/analyze always bump in one grouped PR; all four blocked dependabot PRs resolved after merge
parent: pm-qwoy
risk: low
confidence: high
resolution: drift-scan uses explicit Stats typing for @types/node 26 compatibility; Dependabot npm updates now wait three days and GitHub Actions updates are grouped.
expected_result: "@types/node 26 PRs can typecheck after rebase, npm dependency PRs avoid pnpm minimum-release-age violations, and CodeQL action init/analyze bump in one grouped PR."
actual_result: Linked pnpm typecheck passed; build/lint/contracts/security/audit and full 100/100/100/100 coverage passed locally. Existing Dependabot PRs still need rebasing or superseding after merge.
