  "2026-07-06T09:17:34.708Z",codex-agent,"Implementation continuation: claimed the canonical Dependabot unblocker after live GH PR checks. Current open Dependabot state still matches the item: #462 fails build/docs on Node type drift, #461 fails cooldown-age install, and #459/#460 split CodeQL action updates. Existing working-tree fixes are being included in the combined PR."
  "2026-07-06T09:26:35.505Z",codex-agent,"Evidence: included Dependabot unblocker fixes after live GH PR check review. drift-scan now uses explicit node:fs Stats typing for @types/node 26 compatibility; dependabot.yml adds npm cooldown.default-days=3 and groups GitHub Actions updates to keep codeql-action init/analyze in lockstep. Linked typecheck passed; pnpm build/lint/contracts passed; security scan and pnpm audit clean; full coverage passed 264 files / 5436 tests / 100% statements branches functions lines."
  "2026-07-06T09:36:21.025Z",codex-agent,"Greptile pre-push review a9feea90-9aae-4b8a-a91b-e0060c889b7c returned one P2 note about pm-changelog manifest declaring schema without an activate hook. Triage: no repo patch applied because this is installed package-owned pm-changelog manifest output, and pm SDK capability derivation intentionally grants schema for command/importer/exporter flag metadata; health shows pm-changelog activation ok with command flag registrations. If package semantics need a clearer declaration, that belongs upstream in pm-changelog."
