close_reason: "Fixed Dependabot CI blockers for Node typings, npm release age, and split CodeQL action bumps"
body: "Fixes applied in working tree (session 2026-07-06):\n- src/core/history/drift-scan.ts: import type { Stats } from node:fs and type the stat value/param explicitly (also normalized fs/promises import to node: prefix). Compatible with @types/node 22 and 26.\n- .github/dependabot.yml: npm ecosystem gains cooldown.default-days: 3 so bumps are older than the pnpm minimum-release-age policy before a PR opens; github-actions ecosystem gains a single all-patterns group so codeql-action init/analyze move in lockstep.\n\nAfter these land on main: dependabot PRs #459/#460 should be superseded by one grouped actions PR; #461 passes once the package ages; #462 passes after rebase picks up the drift-scan fix."
